the state for the cost

00:04:28.190 --> 00:04:29.270 align:middle line:90%
of the photovoltaics.

00:04:29.270 --> 00:04:30.770 align:middle line:84%
So the photovoltaics
are, in effect,

00:04:30.770 --> 00:04:34.570 align:middle line:90%
paid for by the rate payers.

00:04:34.570 --> 00:04:39.620 align:middle line:84%
So photovoltaics has come
a tremendously long way.

00:04:39.620 --> 00:04:41.920 align:middle line:84%
Right now, all of our
photovoltaics have been

00:04:41.920 --> 00:04:44.920 align:middle line:84%
