00:31:42.570 --> 00:31:43.480 align:middle line:90%
>>They're tapped out.

00:31:43.480 --> 00:31:46.320 align:middle line:84%
>>They're tapped out, and they
don't have the business skills.

00:31:46.320 --> 00:31:48.200 align:middle line:90%
They're innovators.

00:31:48.200 --> 00:31:50.950 align:middle line:84%
And so what's needed
is a group of people

00:31:50.950 --> 00:31:55.990 align:middle line:84%
that can kind of incubate that
idea, and at the same time

00:31:55.990 --> 00:31:59.850 align:middle line:84%
that an idea is being developed,
do some market research,

00:31:59.850 --> 00:32:02.289 align:middle line:84%
see is there even a
need for this device,

00:32:02.289 --> 00:32:03.830 align:middle line:84%
because a lot of
people invent things

00:32:03.830 --> 00:32:05.240 align:middle line:90%
where there's no market for it.

00:32:05.240 --> 00:32:08.720 align:middle line:84%
It's just nifty,
it's a nifty thing.

00:32:08.720 --> 00:32:11.170 align:middle line:84%
So our group is
basically market driven.

00:32:11.170 --> 00:32:14.370 align:middle line:84%
We have one foot
in the marketplace

00:32:14.370 --> 00:32:19.640 align:middle line:84%
and so we know that if we
