00:32:19.640 --> 00:32:23.610 align:middle line:84%
device for remote
areas of the world,

00:32:23.610 --> 00:32:25.150 align:middle line:90%
we have a massive market.

00:32:25.150 --> 00:32:27.870 align:middle line:90%
We can demonstrate that.

00:32:27.870 --> 00:32:29.430 align:middle line:90%
So that's the problem.

00:32:29.430 --> 00:32:38.550 align:middle line:84%
